OL,3,CCharles Hanson claims his
OL,4,C'controlling' wife left him 'a beaten
OL,5,Cand broken man'
OL,7,FTV auctioneer Charles Hanson has
OL,8,Fclaimed he was "almost a slave" to his
OL,9,Fwife, who left him "a beaten and
OL,10,Fbroken man" by controlling him and
OL,11,Fmaking him subservient to her.
OL,13,FThe 46-year-old Bargain Hunt and
OL,14,FAntiques Road Trip star told Derby
OL,15,FCrown Court his wife Rebecca Hanson
OL,16,Fwas allowed "to do what she wanted"
OL,17,Fbut would not let him watch TV in bed,
OL,18,Fand falsely accused him of having
OL,19,Fathlete's foot.
