OL,4,C'controlling' wife left him 'a beaten
OL,5,Cand broken man'
OL,7,FHis trial has heard that he is accused
OL,8,Fof using violence towards Mrs Hanson
OL,9,Fover a 10-year period, including
OL,10,Fpushing, scratching and grabbing her.
OL,12,FHanson, of Ashbourne Road in
OL,13,FMackworth, Derby, denies controlling
OL,14,For coercive behaviour, assault
OL,15,Foccasioning actual bodily harm, and
OL,16,Fassault by beating, charges brought
OL,17,Fafter he was arrested in June 2023.
