OL,7,FDuring his second day of evidence to
OL,8,Fthe court, Hanson denied trying to
OL,9,Fportray his wife as being mentally ill
OL,10,F` saying she experienced "moments and
OL,11,Fepisodes" including an incident in
OL,12,Fwhich she claimed his legs being
OL,13,Fcrossed amounted to abuse.
OL,15,FUnder cross-examination from
OL,16,Fprosecutor Stephen Kemp on Monday,
OL,17,FHanson told jurors he had a stammer as
OL,18,Fa young boy and that he is "actually a
OL,19,Fvery nervous man" whose "facade" might
OL,20,Fsuggest he is more confident than he
OL,21,Freally is.
