OL,7,FQuestioned as to why he sent messages
OL,8,Fto his wife, including one conceding
OL,9,Fhe had a bad temper, Hanson claimed he
OL,10,Fhad "literally tapped every word she
OL,11,Fwanted to hear" about "lost temper,
OL,12,Fanger management and 'completely my
OL,13,Ffault'".
OL,15,FAsserting that the messages were "not
OL,16,Fthe truth" but instead an attempt to
OL,17,Ftell his wife what she wanted to hear,
OL,18,FHanson told the court: "I was under
OL,19,Fthe control of Rebecca. She completely
OL,20,Fridiculed me, told me that I was
OL,21,Frubbish every day.
