OL,7,FAs well as accusing him of abuse,
OL,8,FHanson said, his wife had turned away
OL,9,Ffrom him at night and said "just go to
OL,10,Fsleep".
OL,12,F"My wife would never, ever give me a
OL,13,Fhug goodnight. She would say most
OL,14,Fnights 'you have got athlete's foot,
OL,15,Fdon't come near me'. I have never had
OL,16,Fathlete's foot," Hanson added.
OL,18,FThe court heard the auctioneer told
OL,19,Fpolice in interviews that his wife was
