OL,7,FHe also wrote a letter to the
OL,8,Fdedicated officer for the
OL,9,Finvestigation in August 2023, saying
OL,10,Fhe had serious doubts about his wife's
OL,11,Freliability and credibility and
OL,12,F"concerns as to her mental health".
OL,14,FHanson's letter, the court heard,
OL,15,Fadded: "Criminal proceedings involving
OL,16,Fcross-examination could be very
OL,17,Fharmful to her mental health.
OL,19,F"In the light of the above I kindly
OL,20,Fask Derbyshire Police to cease their
OL,21,Finvestigation."
