OL,7,FAt the time of the letter to police,
OL,8,FHanson said, he had taken legal advice
OL,9,Fand was "two months into having been
OL,10,Farrested at my home for an alleged
OL,11,Fdomestic incident which never
OL,12,Fhappened".
