OL,7,F"There was never an attempted
OL,8,Fstrangulation, let alone a headlock."
OL,10,FAsked by Mr Kemp if his position was
OL,11,Fthat his wife had lied to the police
OL,12,Fand "came to the court to lie", Hanson
OL,13,Ftold the court: "It's a very difficult
OL,14,Fquestion to answer but, yes, there are
OL,15,Fnumerous lies in my wife's statements."
OL,17,FHanson, who will continue his evidence
OL,18,Fon Tuesday, said his wife "can be a
OL,19,Ffantasist" and "dream up crazy
OL,20,Fsuggestions which are far from the
OL,21,Ftruth".
